     Code      | Name
     --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

     Abbreviations Used:
     EA        : External Assessment
     IA        : Internal Assessment
     PR        : Practical
     VV        : Viva-Voce
     TH        : Theory
     Cr        : Credit
     X         : PAST APPEARANCE
     *         : Grace applied
     ABP       : Absent but passed
     P         : Pass
     F         : Fail
     STS       : RESULT STATUS
     RMK       : REMARK/S
     PRS       : PREVIOUS RESULT STAND
     Re        : Re-appear
     RLA       : Result Late due to Awards
     UM        : UNFAIR MEANS
     Fr        : Fresher
     GP        : Grade Point
     SGPA      : Semester Grade Point Average
     CGPA      : Cumulative Grade Point Average
     f         : Full
     I         : Improvement
     --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
